{"tid":1535963,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"「子喉歌后」冼劍麗肺炎病逝，享年89歲。","createTime":"2019-09-03T14:06:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-03T16:39:44.000Z","uid":35221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"e042a37e4ec7cb00892ea10571e134f8a01d5902","tid":1535963,"uid":35221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T14:06:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190903/large/1567519030_74ac.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190903%2Flarge%2F1567519030_74ac.jpg&h=84d403a3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有「子喉歌后」之稱的前輩歌手冼劍麗，上月6日因肺炎在廣華醫院病逝，享年89歲。將於本月6日假紅磡萬國殯儀館舉行喪禮，以基督教儀式進行安息禮拜後，遺體運往歌連臣角火化。<br />\n<br />\n1956年憑歌曲《一縷柔情》走紅的冼劍麗，是當代著名的歌伶，曾出版逾120張唱片，她的的唱腔盪氣迴腸，音樂造詣頗高，除擅長演唱粵曲和粵語流行曲外，還對京劇、錫劇、黃梅調及西曲均有涉獵。被封為「子喉歌后」的她，更進軍影壇拍攝電影，作品包括：《黛玉葬花》、《珠樓錯》等，還曾跟胡楓和羅艷卿合作拍《大家姐》，胡楓接受傳媒訪問表示大家多年未見面，對她的離世感到惋惜。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20190903/60006537\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190903%2F60006537&d=wLht58ApaBOsBOdSjqbSDeQdxvW7LhoH5lY2nOShEJQ%3D&h=baa3bfba\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190903%2F60006537&h=2b5d3c92\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20190903/60006537</a>"},{"pid":"3dc1b8e9bb422aaf70f05adcb3aad9973c53b6ab","tid":1535963,"uid":35221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T14:06:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://www.operapreview.com/media/k2/items/cache/140b010967f6cad065f658f2e2e7cc8d_XL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.operapreview.com%2Fmedia%2Fk2%2Fitems%2Fcache%2F140b010967f6cad065f658f2e2e7cc8d_XL.jpg&h=e380d359&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.operapreview.com/images/2019.9%E7%B6%B2%E9%A0%81/%E6%9C%80%E6%96%B0%E8%B3%87%E8%A8%8A/%E5%86%BC%E5%8A%8D%E9%BA%97%E8%BE%AD%E4%B8%96/sin06%20%E6%8B%B7%E8%B2%9D.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.operapreview.com%2Fimages%2F2019.9%25E7%25B6%25B2%25E9%25A0%2581%2F%25E6%259C%2580%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%25B3%2587%25E8%25A8%258A%2F%25E5%2586%25BC%25E5%258A%258D%25E9%25BA%2597%25E8%25BE%25AD%25E4%25B8%2596%2Fsin06%2520%25E6%258B%25B7%25E8%25B2%259D.jpg&h=1b47897c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n名伶冼劍麗本名冼菁華，經於八月六日下午在廣華醫院因肺炎與世長辭，享年八十九歲。九月六日上午十一時半至下午二時，假紅磡萬國殯儀館三樓慈恩堂舉行基督教安息禮拜，送別一代名伶。遺體隨即送往歌連臣角火化。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.operapreview.com/images/2019.9%E7%B6%B2%E9%A0%81/%E6%9C%80%E6%96%B0%E8%B3%87%E8%A8%8A/%E5%86%BC%E5%8A%8D%E9%BA%97%E8%BE%AD%E4%B8%96/sin07%20%E6%8B%B7%E8%B2%9D.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.operapreview.com%2Fimages%2F2019.9%25E7%25B6%25B2%25E9%25A0%2581%2F%25E6%259C%2580%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%25B3%2587%25E8%25A8%258A%2F%25E5%2586%25BC%25E5%258A%258D%25E9%25BA%2597%25E8%25BE%25AD%25E4%25B8%2596%2Fsin07%2520%25E6%258B%25B7%25E8%25B2%259D.jpg&h=78405058&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n冼劍麗成名於五十年代，有「子喉歌后」美譽，唱腔神似芳腔，她的音樂造詣非常卓越，除粵曲及粵語歌曲外，京劇、錫劇、黃梅調以及歐西流行曲均有涉獵，粵語流行曲《一縷柔情》更是風靡海內外，是為代表作。又曾参演多部電影，灌錄唱片百餘張，作品豐富。伊人已逝，音容宛在，她清越嘹亮的歌聲，更使人倍添懷念。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.operapreview.com/index.php/網上雜誌/最新資訊/item/1272-一代名伶冼劍麗辭世\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.operapreview.com%2Findex.php%2F%E7%B6%B2%E4%B8%8A%E9%9B%9C%E8%AA%8C%2F%E6%9C%80%E6%96%B0%E8%B3%87%E8%A8%8A%2Fitem%2F1272-%E4%B8%80%E4%BB%A3%E5%90%8D%E4%BC%B6%E5%86%BC%E5%8A%8D%E9%BA%97%E8%BE%AD%E4%B8%96&d=wLht58ApaBOsBOdSjqbSDeQdxvW7LhoH5lY2nOShEJQ%3D&h=25b8ed1a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.operapreview.com/index.php/網上雜誌/最新資訊/item/1272-一代名伶冼劍麗辭世</a>"},{"pid":"9e1d5b82e4e43e036e2aba498b7ec771cb4ba67d","tid":1535963,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T14:0